org.hibernate.search.backend

Interface IndexWorkVisitor<P,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - Context parameter type expected by a specific visitor
    R - Return type provided by a specific visitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IndexUpdateVisitor, StreamingOperationExecutorSelector, TransactionalOperationExecutorSelector

    public interface IndexWorkVisitor<P,R>
    Contract for visitors of LuceneWork types.

    Implementations can receive a specific input parameter and return a specific output type. Use Void as parameterization for each of the two not needed.

    Author:
    Sanne Grinovero, Gunnar Morling
